#. Max bytes: 73
msgctxt "Offset_0x2E0_Len_73"
msgid "I was surprised that you came for me,\nbut it also made me really happy..."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 69
msgctxt "Offset_0x4B0_Len_69"
msgid "I realized that you're the Prince Charming\nwho's going to protect me."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 70
msgctxt "Offset_0x670_Len_70"
msgid "This might be the first time...\nthat I've felt this way about someone."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 86
msgctxt "Offset_0x830_Len_86"
msgid "Idols aren't allowed to be in romantic relationships...\nSo I figured I'd say this now."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 53
msgctxt "Offset_0xA00_Len_53"
msgid "Kiryu-san... this is the present I mentioned earlier."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 25
msgctxt "Offset_0xC20_Len_25"
msgid "...I love you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 48
msgctxt "Offset_0xD90_Len_48"
msgid "Please don't ever stop being my Prince Charming."
msgstr ""

